query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ab_test_campaign_assignments` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `testId` int NOT NULL,
  `variantId` int NOT NULL,
  `campaignId` int NOT NULL,
  `assignedAt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_ab_test_campaign_assignments_testId` (`testId`),
  KEY `idx_ab_test_campaign_assignments_variantId` (`variantId`),
  KEY `idx_ab_test_campaign_assignments_campaignId` (`campaignId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
